item.description:
The picture I posted for this meeting is the map. Click on it to view it larger.

On the left of the graphic is the meeting point, look for the word Park in RED on the left of the picture.

The better known parking lot for the lake, by the baseball field, is on the right hand side of the picture, just off the rotary - the red round circle. There's about 3 miles from the rotary to the meetup spot.
